  "texts": [
    "This technique, often combined with normalization, is used in various federated learning models to standardize the input data and enhance the model performance and accuracy.",
    "The log-transformation method is particularly useful for handling skewed data.",
    "It can stabilize the variance and normalize distributions, making the statistical analysis more robust.",
    "Moreover, Log transformation is widely used in financial modelling and other areas where data scalability is considered an important factor.",
